<lyrics>[V1]
 Vawleicung sifahnak kha na hmuh tikah, Na ruahchannak kha a dongh
 dengmang ahcun, Thachin pakhat hnu pakhat na rel lai i Pathian nih tampi
 an pek kha na hngalh lai.

[C1]
   Thachin pakhat hnu pakhat rel tuah, A tampi an pek kha na hngalh
   lai; Thachin rel tuah, pakhat hnu pakhat, Pathian nih zeitluk an dawt kha
   na hngalh lai.

[V2]
 Si tha mirum mi kha na hmuh tik hna ah, Jesuh nih pek an duhmi thil
 kha va ruat, Chaw in na cawk khawh lo na co awk thil kha, Vancung ah na
 hmuh lai mi kha, va ruat tuah.

[C2]
   Thachin pakhat hnu pakhat rel tuah, A tampi an pek kha na hngalh
   lai; Thachin rel tuah, pakhat hnu pakhat, Pathian nih zeitluk an dawt kha
   na hngalh lai.

[V3]
 Harnak le sifahnak na cung tlung hmanhseh, Thachin pakhat hnu pakhat
 va rel than tuah, Lungfehnak le thachin a si tiah ruat ko, Kannih
 thiannak ca harnak kha a herh ve.

[C3]
   Thachin pakhat hnu pakhat rel tuah, A tampi an pek kha na hngalh
   lai; Thachin rel tuah, pakhat hnu pakhat, Pathian nih zeitluk an dawt kha
   na hngalh lai.

[V4]
 Ngaih-chiatnak kha tlung hmanhseh, Zeihmanh va phang hlah Pathian nih
 laksawng tha nangmah ca a chiah. Khuadawm le nitlang vawlei ca a that
 bang Minung thatnak caah khuadawm kha a herh.

[C4]
   Thachin pakhat hnu pakhat rel tuah, A tampi an pek kha na hngalh
   lai; Thachin rel tuah, pakhat hnu pakhat, Pathian nih zeitluk an dawt kha
   na hngalh lai.</lyrics>
<key>Eb</key>
<title>THA CHIN KHA REL TUAH CH354</title>
</song>